snippet.title: CarX Drift Racing 3: Release Trailer
snippet.description:
CarX Drift Racing 3: Release Trailer

What's up, drivers! 
CarX Drift Racing 3 is now available on iOS and Google Play! 
Enjoy! 

AppStore: https://apps.apple.com/app/apple-store/id1569386864?pt=118485357&ct=YouTube&mt=8
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.carxtech.carxdr3
